{"tid":1840061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（留名找數）「黃經圈」和你捐利是","createTime":"2020-01-24T16:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T20:39:28.000Z","uid":204656,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7f1715428992b26c4d610c4e44c44375eb8a4e","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"新年除左教親戚細路講<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span><br />\n收到藍絲利是應該點處置好呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我決定全數利是捐出去</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n收到藍絲利是唔知點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生冇錢又想捐錢幫人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星火凍結左7000萬點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港首次和你捐利是</span></span>上線啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左要將活動帶起潮流趨勢 懇請大家幫一個忙 用自己ig自發tag人 款項不定 講心唔講金 唔洗鬥捐多捐少 老少咸宜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBXZYty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBXZYty.jpg&h=670a5921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（記得遮個人資料）<br />\n記得tag曬你最黃嘅fd   有剩記得幫襯下黃店呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">初四找數</span></span>"},{"pid":"09a7fc74bd361b6a6b8fef7c12d56ca4c4815448","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fbffe77c8562ab07c1d553b1ac072a4bb1e0e709","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"樓主好波"},{"pid":"83004fc8b91ee340bd3598a35999810232d517cc","tid":1840061,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"全靠抗爭者，中國人先減少來港，肺炎傳染程度先減少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1833923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1833923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d630fdc2192d2a380a3b184b7889f4c3b18a4c3c","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"Good night sir"},{"pid":"5a035bba104a19c3495b9fef0508bd6d3a357683","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c758863d2687723dccf2d1840f438abb0e661c94","tid":1840061,"uid":285120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"913515cedc377e27359652276cf5429a7c01ab71","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"推文記得戴口罩"},{"pid":"62763084244da263aacca6420f17ad09b2668a9f","tid":1840061,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkg